he load backup box, browse for the backup file and submit.</td></tr><tr><td width="20%"> <strong>Browse</strong></td><td>Click here to search for your config_backup.bin backup file. Just submit the file to restore your settings.</td></tr></table></div></article></div></div> <% include ../../_partials/content/_bluenav-1080p-webUI-mobile.ejs %><footer> <% include ../../_partials/amp/_amp-footer.ejs %></footer></body></html>